 "name": "RPlog_Sabrina_s_Capture_by_Boba_Fett",
 "title": "Sabrina's Capture by Boba Fett",
 "summary": "In Coruscant's Parliamentary District, the Jedi padawan Sabrina Rheatis is ambushed by the bounty hunter Boba Fett, who has already abducted the Jedi Brandis and Ai'kani and means to add her to his haul for the Empire. Sabrina mentally triggers the complex's alarms and desperately calls out through the Force to Luke Skywalker as she wrestles Fett's rifle from his grip and flees down the stairs. A running battle ensues amid panicking crowds and arriving guards, with Fett deploying his flamethrower, grappling cord, and a rocket while Sabrina returns fire and severs his snares. In the final grapple Fett pins her, smashing her head against the permacrete; she cracks his visor with the rifle butt before losing consciousness, and the hunter injects her with the Force-suppressing sedative and rockets off with another captured Jedi, Luke never having appeared.",
